=== Technical Architecture
@startuml DGraph

' Frontend Applications
RECTANGLE_STYLE ReactJS_Storefront
ReactJS_Storefront : ReactJS Storefront
ReactJS_Storefront --> API_Gateway : Sends Requests

RECTANGLE_STYLE Angular_Backoffice
Angular_Backoffice : Angular Backoffice
Angular_Backoffice --> API_Gateway : Manages Backoffice Operations

' API Gateway
RECTANGLE_STYLE API_Gateway
API_Gateway : Routes Requests to Services

' Microservices
RECTANGLE_STYLE IdentityService
IdentityService : Handles Authentication

RECTANGLE_STYLE UserService
UserService : Manages User Profiles

RECTANGLE_STYLE CustomerService
CustomerService : Manages Customer Data

RECTANGLE_STYLE ProductService
ProductService : Manages Product Catalog

RECTANGLE_STYLE InventoryService
InventoryService : Tracks Inventory Levels

RECTANGLE_STYLE OrderService
OrderService : Handles Orders

RECTANGLE_STYLE PaymentService
PaymentService : Processes Payments

' Connections from API Gateway to Microservices
API_Gateway --> IdentityService
API_Gateway --> UserService
API_Gateway --> ProductService
API_Gateway --> OrderService
API_Gateway --> PaymentService
API_Gateway --> InventoryService

' Microservice Dependencies
IdentityService --> UserService : Validates User Tokens
CustomerService --> UserService : Fetches User Details
OrderService --> CustomerService : Retrieves Customer Info
OrderService --> ProductService : Fetches Product Data
OrderService --> PaymentService : Handles Payment Workflow
ProductService --> InventoryService : Checks Stock Availability

@enduml
